            "title": "奧運站帝柏海灣3房套以$1,675萬獲承接 持貨約25年轉手帳面賺約$1,212萬 (另有本日最新成交)",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aSk_3nyWLVPnCOYC8ZZuAQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/28hse_com_210/8b72075fe60ad88966c2533783a38657\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
