            "title": "財經｜迅銷(06288)中期多賺兩成 上調全年盈利預測",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜迅銷(06288)中期多賺兩成 上調全年盈利預測\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜迅銷(06288)中期多賺兩成 上調全年盈利預測</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">經營UNIQLO的<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"迅銷集團\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:迅銷集團;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/迅銷集團\">迅銷集團</a>(06288)公布截至2月底止中期業績，股東應佔溢利2792.9億日圓，按年增長19.6%，派息320日圓。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">迅銷集團修訂2026財年全年度業績預測，收益上調至3.9萬億日圓，較原預測增加2.6%；經營溢利總額預測上調至7000億日圓，較原預測增加7.7%。股東應佔溢利預測升至4800億日圓，較原預測增長6.7%。集團目前預估年末股息320日圓，合計全年度派發640日圓，每股將較上年度增派140日圓。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">集團上半年綜合收益總額2.06萬億日圓，按年增長14.8%，經營溢利4006.66億日圓，按年增長31.7%。</p></div>",
